reviewText: This is an awesome look into the world of competition bbq, please support this these guys and pick this one up! Read my full review of this here http://www.wrensbbq.tv/episode-018-review-american-smoke-dvd
If you love BBQ and want a behind the scenes look at competition then this is what you're looking for.  Interviews with pros gives you a good insight into the world of Competition BBQ.
